# --- OpenFOAM / blastFoam run artifacts -----------------------------------
# Local end-to-end test runs (huge mesh / processor* artifacts).
_e2e_runs/
# Timestamped cases generated by the GUI's "Run" button (Case_<dim>_<YYYYMMDD>_<HHMMSS>/).
# Reference cases like building3D/ and mappedBuilding3D/ stay tracked.
Case_1D_[0-9]*/
Case_2D_[0-9]*/
Case_3D_[0-9]*/

# --- Transient files used by the agent / scripts --------------------------
_commit_msg.txt
_inspect_*.sh
_test_*.py
*.bak
*.tmp
